blog.name: bringbackgenisvellandphylavell
blog.title: Bring back Genis and Phyla Vell
blog.description:
Site dedicated to all things Genis-Vell and Phyla-Vell. Former Captains Marvel and son and daughter of the original one, Mar-Vell. They were killed off very soon by Marvel and they deserve a second chance, we don't ask about a new chance as Captains Marvel but to come back to the Cosmic Marvel Universe (Quasar, Photon, Legacy, Martyr, whatever). 

Posts about Genis and Phyla. Mar-Vell, Rick Jones, Guardians of the Galaxy, Adam Warlock, Quasar, Thanos, Starlin stuff, some Avengers and a lot of Cosmic stuff. Welcome!

summary: A new design for the Captain Marvel uniform, Carol Danvers. I was not happy with my previous design... I am a fan of Carol...
caption: A new design for the Captain Marvel uniform, Carol Danvers. I was not happy with my previous design… I am a fan of Carol Danvers of the old school, I have read even the old comics written by Claremont, I have always thought that she is a wonderful character, but I’m still sad because Carol Danvers will never be “ms marvel” in the movie. Maybe even in comics, a part of her past is suppressed, it’s a matter of waiting and seeing what happens

title: Captain Marvel: Carol Danvers, Nick Fury ed un mucchio di nuovi dettagli dal film!
body:
Captain Marvel: Carol Danvers, Nick Fury ed un mucchio di nuovi dettagli dal film!

Captain Marvel sarà il primo blockbuster a conduzione femminile dei Marvel Studios, ed è chiaro che, sopratutto grazie a pellicole come Wonder Woman, l’aspettativa verso la pellicola è alta, infatti ci sono molti fan (noi compresi), che non vedono l’ora di vederla. Il film è comprensibilmente “l’obiettivo di marketing” di questo mese Empire Magazine di questo mese, e grazie al loro ultimo numero…

summary:
I fear for marvels captain marvel movie.
It looks like a spectacle, a great movie and visually beautiful with generic marvel...
body:
I fear for marvels captain marvel movie.

It looks like a spectacle, a great movie and visually beautiful with generic marvel humour. It will be enjoyable yes.

But captain marvel herself in the trailers seems to lack personality. Like, I’m fearing marvel have gone for the good ol ‘badass 2d female character’ where her entire personality is 'i can do shit’.

Which seems to be a trope for many modern female characters tbh. Badass but with no flaws or personality because of fear she won’t be badass enough
